<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_364" id="181r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_364_r1l25">Görgen <expan>ʒolln<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> Rotenſteın </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_364_r1l27"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Görg als Jr vns nehſt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_364_r1l26">vnd yecʒ </ab></add> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von eẅrs knechts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_364_r1l28"><expan>Concʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> wıe Jm geleyt bey vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſagt</expan> ſey <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> etc das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_364_r1l29">haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd haben mıt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> lıeben <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_364_r1l30"><expan>Ratgeſelle<ex>n</ex></expan> . <expan>Sebold<ex>en</ex></expan> pfıncʒıng der dıe ʒeıt <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>meıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> ſol <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_364_r1l31">ſeyn . <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt . der hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> / daʒ Jm dauon nıht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_364_r1l32">wıſſend ſey . So wıſſen wır auch ſelb mıt eẅch vnd <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_364_r1l33"><expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> knecht . <expan cert="unknown">C</expan> . ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex>heıt</expan> nıht ʒu ſchıken </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_364_r1l34">haben denn gut / Weſt <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> Jr <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> eẅr knecht </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_365" id="181v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r2l1"><expan>keın<ex>en</ex></expan> der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . dıe eẅch ın <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuſſ</expan> <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> vor den Jr in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r2l2"><expan>ſorge<ex>n</ex></expan> weͣrt / Das möcht Jr vns ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> tun / ſo <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r2l3"><expan>derſelbe<ex>n</ex></expan> der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> rede <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> hören / vnd eẅch <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r2l4"><expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_365_r2l8">vnd das <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> wır eẅch nehſt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_365_r2l7">auch alſo </ab></add> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / do was <expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_365_r2l9">von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> da der antwurt an vns vordert </ab></add> Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan> das teten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r2l6">wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Cırcu<ex>m</ex>cıſıo<ex>n</ex>ıs</expan> <expan>dom<ex>in</ex>j</expan> Anno etc <expan>S<ex>e</ex>c<ex>un</ex>do</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_364" id="181r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Görgen <expan>Zolln<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> Rotenstein</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Görg, als ir uns nehst <add>und yecz</add>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von ewrs knechts
                                <expan>Concze<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, wie im geleyt bey uns
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sagt</expan> sey <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.,
                        das haben wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und haben mit
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> lieben <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>ratgeselle<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Sebold<ex>en</ex></expan> Pfinczing, der die zeit
                                <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>meist<ex>er</ex></expan> sol
                                <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> seyn, <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        geredt, der hat uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, daz im davon niht
                        wissend sey. So wissen wir auch selb mit ewch und
                            <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> knecht <expan cert="unknown">C<ex>oncz</ex></expan> zu disen <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> in
                                <expan>sund<ex>er</ex>heit</expan> niht zu schiken haben denn gut,
                        west <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> ir <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> <pb facs="#facs_365" id="181v"/> ewr knecht <expan>kein<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die ewch in
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuss</expan>
<expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> vor den ir in <expan>sorge<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        weͣrt, das möcht ir uns zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> tun, so
                                <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>derselbe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> rede <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> hören und ewch <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
                        auch <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>; <add>und das
                                <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewch nehst <add>auch also</add>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, do was <expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
                            von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> da der antwurt an uns vordert</add>. Denn
                        wo wir ewch lieb <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan>, das teten wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>circu<ex>m</ex>cisio<ex>n</ex>is</expan>
<expan>dom<ex>in</ex>i</expan> anno etc.
                            <expan>s<ex>e</ex>c<ex>un</ex>do</expan>.</ab>
</div>
